Class Habit

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cmput301f17t07.ingroove.Model.Habit
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Identifiable, java.io.Serializable

    public class Habit
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, Identifiable
    [Data Class] Representing a recurring action to be done. Habits have names and optional descriptions. They may repeat at regular intervals each week, but can only occur once a day.
    See Also:
    Identifiable, Created by fraserbulbuc on 2017-10-17., Serialized Form
